<br>
The only thing you have going in your favor is that you're only level 40 and I'm going to assume that you don't know a few things, haven't quite yet grasped the concept of strategy and game play.<br>
<br>
Here's a little tip for you, if you hit a mezzed mob, the mez breaks.  Depending on the circumstances leading up to the mezzing of said mob, said mob will typically go straight for the enchanter, especially if no one bothered to taunt a bit, due to the fact that everyone was just randomly hitting any mob in sight.<br>
<br>
My main is a melee, my secondary is an enchanter.  I type 90+ wpm.  Therefore, I can tell you quite comfortably that, especially with you yahoo's breaking mez repeatedly, she didn't have TIME to tell you what was going on, because you weren't allowing her to do her job in the first place.<br>
<br>
