<br>
Playing this game requires a bit more then running up to a mob and hitting /a .  Since it's obvious you don't understand that, I'd have gated on you too.  <br>
<br>
My tips for you today?<br>
<br>
Learn what a main assist is.  Learn how enchanters can most benefit your group and work with them accordingly.  Take a step back and instead of laying the blame at some convenient character's feet, accept the fact that no one in this group appears to have been blameless, with the possible exception of the enchanter trying to do her job and giving up in frustration.<br>
<br>
